title: SAMSUNG Galaxy Tab A T385 2 GB RAM 16 GB ROM 8 inch with Wi-Fi+4G Tablet (Black)

product_specification.Additional Features: Smart Switch (PC Version), Available User Memory: 9.7 GB
product_specification.Sales Package: Tablet, Travel Adapter, USB Cable, Quick Start Guide, Warranty Card
product_specification.Bluetooth Profiles: A2DP, AVRCP, DI, HFP, HID, HOGP, HSP, MAP, OPP, PAN, PBAP
product_specification.Video Formats Supported: MP4, M4V, 3GP, 3G2, WMV, ASF, AVI, FLV, MKV, WEBM
product_specification.Audio Formats Supported: MP3, M4A, 3GA, AAC, OGG, OGA, WAV, WMA, AMR, AWB, FLAC, MID, MIDI, XMF, MXMF, IMY, RTTTL, RTX, OTA
product_specification.Warranty Summary: 1 Year on Tablet, 6 Months on Accessories

product_description.Lightweight Metal Design: Its smooth edges along with its metal back add to its aesthetic appeal.
product_description.20.32 cm (8) Display: Enjoy an immersive viewing experience by enhancing your movie watching time with a bright display, even when you're out in the sun.
product_description.5000 mAh Battery: You can stay connected and entertained by binge watching your favourite shows and movies as it offers up to 14 continuous hours of video viewing.
product_description.Bixby Home for Convenience: Access your favourite apps, content and all the information by simply pressing the Bixby button.
product_description.Game Launcher: Store your favourite and most-played games in one place, and mute all other alerts to enjoy an exciting gaming experience.
product_description.Capture Life's Best Moments: Its 8 MP rear camera, with an aperture ratio of f/1.9 and an LED flash, lets you capture picture-perfect photos even in low-light conditions. With its 5 MP front camera, you can click gorgeous selfies.
product_description.Glitch-free Performance: Powered by a 1.4 GHz quad-core processor and 2 GB of RAM, you can seamlessly multitask and run multiple apps without any lag.
product_description.Other Features: The Android Nougat OS offers an easy user experience and lets you multitask like a pro with its split screen feature.
